snippet.title: TGA Candidacy Video: A Story That Never Grows Dull | Honkai: Star Rail
snippet.description:
These people, these places... They appear familiar at first sight, and will never grow dull.

Thanks to all your support, Honkai: Star Rail has won Best Mobile Game at The Game Awards 2023. Your companionship gives true meaning to the continuation of our journey.

English Voice:
Black Swan——Arryn Zech
Acheron——Allegra Clark
